{{Han etyl}}

{{Han compound|止|凵|ls=ic|t1=foot|t2=cave}} – to step out of a cave; to exit. Compare {{zh-l|*各}}.

By the {{w|Qin dynasty}}, the character has lost its original shape. Based on the distorted form, ''{{w|Shuowen}}'' mistakenly interprets the character as a {{liushu|p|nocap=1}} of a plant growing outwards.

